@startuml
title Module Pipeline - Temporal Extraction and Reasoning
left to right direction

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Extraction flow" as FLOW
folder "data/processed" as PROC
folder "data/exports/temporals" as TMPX

package "src.temporal" {
  component "temporal_extractor.py" as EX
  component "date_normaliser.py" as DN
  component "heideltime_client.py" as HT
  component "reasoner.py" as RSN
}

component "Regex temporal parser" as RGX
component "Engine selector\n(regex | heideltime)" as SEL

FLOW --> EX
PROC --> EX
EX --> SEL

SEL --> RGX : default/fallback path
SEL --> HT : when --engine heideltime

RGX --> DN
HT --> DN
DN --> TMPX

TMPX --> RSN
RSN --> TMPX : consistency notes/issues

note right of RSN
Reasoner checks temporal validity,
ordering, and contradiction signals.
end note

@enduml
